---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Noam Lamdan"
	description="Noam Lamdan is a real estate sales representative based in Toronto with more than 20 years of experience."
	pubDate={new Date('October 29 2025')}
		heroImage="https://blog.noamlamdan-ca-664.workers.dev/noam-lamdan.jpg"
>
	<style>
    :root{--accent:#0b74de;--muted:#666;--bg:#f7f9fb}
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{font-family:Inter,system-ui,Arial,sans-serif;margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:#222}
    .wrap{max-width:980px;margin:28px auto;padding:20px}
    header{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:center}
    header img{width:120px;height:120px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(12,12,12,0.1)}
    h1{margin:0;font-size:28px}
    p.lead{color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px}

    .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;gap:20px;margin-top:22px}
    .card{background:#fff;padding:18px;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(12,12,12,0.04)}
    .bio-title{color:var(--accent);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
    .meta{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px}

    .skills{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .chip{background:#eef6ff;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px;color:#0457a6}

    /* timeline */
    .timeline{margin-top:14px}
    .timeline-item{display:flex;gap:12px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f3f5}
    .timeline-item:last-child{border-bottom:0}
    .timeline-year{font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);width:84px}
    .cta{margin-top:14px}
    .btn{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block}

    /* bios grid */
    .bios{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:12px}
    .bios .card{padding:14px}

    /* contact box */
    .contact{position:sticky;top:24px}
    .contact table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
    .contact th{width:90px;text-align:left;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;padding:6px}

    footer{text-align:center;color:var(--muted);margin:28px 0}

    @media (max-width:900px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.bios{grid-template-columns:1fr}.contact{position:static}}
  </style>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Noam Lamdan",
    "jobTitle": "Real Estate Sales Representative",
    "worksFor": {"@type":"Organization","name":"Maple Crest Realty"},
    "alumniOf": {"@type":"CollegeOrUniversity","name":"University of Toronto"},
    "address": {"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Toronto","addressRegion":"ON","addressCountry":"CA"}
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542744173-8e7e53415bb0?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&s=6f9d2f6b2a2d4c8f9d0a1b2c3d4e5f6a" alt="Noam Lamdan portrait">
      <div>
        <h1>Noam Lamdan</h1>
        <div class="meta">Toronto • Sales Representative • Maple Crest Realty</div>
        <p class="lead">Over 20 years of experience guiding buyers and sellers across Toronto’s residential market — strategic, client-first, community-minded.</p>
        <div class="cta"><a class="btn" href="#contact">Schedule a consultation</a></div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">
      <main>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="bio-title">Professional Snapshot</div>
          <p>Noam Lamdan has spent over 20 years working in Toronto real estate, helping clients buy and sell residential properties. Before entering real estate, he worked in sales at Northern Edge Communications, where he built strong client relationships and negotiation skills. He holds a business administration degree from the University of Toronto and stays engaged in real estate industry organizations. Outside of work, Noam enjoys outdoor activities like cycling and golf and regularly volunteers with Habitat for Humanity Toronto.</p>

          <div class="bio-title" style="margin-top:14px">Core strengths</div>
          <div class="skills">
            <span class="chip">Residential Sales</span>
            <span class="chip">Market Analysis</span>
            <span class="chip">Negotiation</span>
            <span class="chip">Client Relations</span>
            <span class="chip">Investment Properties</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bios">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="bio-title">Career Journey</div>
            <p>Noam began his professional career in corporate sales at Northern Edge Communications before finding his calling in real estate. Over two decades, he has developed a reputation for thoughtful market guidance and strong negotiation outcomes for clients.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="bio-title">Education & Associations</div>
            <p>Noam holds a Bachelor’s degree in Business Administration from the University of Toronto and is an active participant in local real estate organizations and industry groups.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="bio-title">Community & Volunteering</div>
            <p>Committed to giving back, Noam volunteers with Habitat for Humanity Toronto and supports initiatives that increase housing access and affordability across the city.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="bio-title">Interests</div>
            <p>When he’s not helping clients, Noam enjoys cycling, playing golf, and exploring Toronto’s neighborhoods and trails.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="bio-title">More short bios (for use on profiles & brochures)</div>
          <ul style="margin:10px 0 0 18px;color:var(--muted)">
            <li>Noam Lamdan has been a part of Toronto’s real estate industry for over 20 years, focusing on residential sales and investment properties.</li>
            <li>For Noam, real estate is about helping people make informed decisions in a competitive market.</li>
            <li>After starting in telecommunications sales, Noam transitioned to real estate where he now provides strategic guidance to buyers and sellers.</li>
            <li>With more than two decades of experience, Noam brings a wealth of knowledge and a client-centered approach to every transaction.</li>
            <li>Noam’s negotiation and market analysis skills help clients achieve stronger outcomes and smoother closings.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card timeline" style="margin-top:12px">
          <div class="bio-title">Professional timeline</div>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-year">2000s</div><div><strong>Northern Edge Communications</strong><div class="meta">Corporate sales — client relations & negotiation</div></div></div>
            <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-year">2005–Present</div><div><strong>Maple Crest Realty</strong><div class="meta">Residential sales, market analysis, and client representation</div></div></div>
            <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-year">Ongoing</div><div><strong>Community work</strong><div class="meta">Volunteer with Habitat for Humanity Toronto and other housing initiatives</div></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </main>

      <aside class="contact">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="bio-title">Contact</div>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr><th>Phone</th><td>+1 (416) 555-0123</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Email</th><td>noam.lamdan@example.com</td></tr>
              <tr><th>Office</th><td>Maple Crest Realty — Toronto, ON</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <div style="margin-top:12px">
            <a class="btn" href="mailto:noam.lamdan@example.com">Email Noam</a>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)">
            <strong>Quick facts</strong>
            <div>20+ years in Toronto real estate</div>
            <div>University of Toronto — BBA</div>
            <div>Volunteer — Habitat for Humanity Toronto</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="height:12px"></div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="bio-title">Social</div>
          <p style="margin:8px 0;color:var(--muted)">Connect on:</p>
          <p style="margin:0"><a href="#">LinkedIn</a> · <a href="#">Instagram</a> · <a href="#">Facebook</a></p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)">© Noam Lamdan • Maple Crest Realty — Trusted Toronto real estate guidance</div>

</Layout>
